Come here, Iâ€™ll tell you the reason behind it. This man or Park Chanyeol is one of a kind. Iâ€™ve never seen any man in this world  who is a complete package like him. No, Iâ€™m not saying heâ€™s perfect cuz HE ISNâ€™T, but he is the closest to perfect. 

He got all the talents in arts and music, heâ€™s the true definition of artists (this could be another essay). He can do anything because he is passionate in everything he does. And, what makes me loves him even more is that he appreciates his fans and treating them like a gold medal. If you donâ€™t know, he once prepared luxury gifts for his fans who came to his birthday party, he had a tattoo about his fansâ€™ anniversary date, and for the past months he went through rough times but he still went around at 5am to see every project his fans had prepared for him on his birthday. Those are just some of his way of showing love.

Yesterday he went to military and will return on September 2022. His fans provide an 18 months project, where there will be an ad at his momentous place, Rodeo Station. Itâ€™ll be showing until he comes back from the military. We (fans) never expected anything from him since heâ€™s been inactive for several months, but he made a promise â€œLetâ€™s meet on every 27thâ€ which means he already prepared this and will post a video every month. Fans prepared 18-months fans support and he prepared 18-months gifts. See, our love is not a one-way boulevard but two-way street. He is so thoughtful about his fans.

I believe thatâ€™s why heâ€™s surrounded by kind and supportive people like his family, best friends, and people who work with him cuz he appreciates everyone. He got all the support and thatâ€™s why I believe he is truly a genuine person. He never fails to prove it and itâ€™s enough for me to keep loving and supporting him.

author: @juicyyy_creaam222
text:
RESEP MEMBUAT DORAYAKI
Bahan yang dibutuhkan:

siapkan 2 butir telur ayam ukuran sedang

siapkan 50 ml susu cair

siapkan Â½ sdt garam dapur

siapkan 150 gram tepung terigu

siapkan 100 gram gula pasir

siapkan Â½ sdm baking powder

siapkan selai coklat atau dark cooking cokelat yang telah dilelehkan sebagai bahan isian

Langkah membuat kue dorayaki:

Kocok dahulu telur ayam dan gula pasir menggunakan mixer sampai mengembang dan benar â€“ benar halus.

Lalu, Anda bisa masukkan susu cair sedikit demi sedikit sambil terus diaduk.

Tambahkan dengan tepung terigu, garam juga baking powder ke dalamnya. Kocok semua bahan tersebut sampai rata dan mengembang lalu matikan mixer.

Siapkan untuk wajan anti lengket untuk memanggang, olesi dengan bahan mentega.

Tuangkan sekitar 1 sdm adonan kulit. Masak hingga bagian bawahnya berubah kecoklatan.

Balik adonan untuk memudahkan memasak sisi yang lain. Masak hingga kurang lebih 30 hingga 45 detik lalu angkat.

Terus buat bagian kulit dorayaki hingga seluruh sampai habis.

Olesi ataupun lumuri selai cokelat pada salah satu sisi kulit dorayaki lalu tumpuk dengan kulit yang lain.

Sekian.. siapa tahu ada yang mau coba buat Yee kan.wkwk
